Description of the table C_PIB_CUSTOMER_EXCLUSIONS

20-Nov-2022

 

Customer Exclusion table is business maintained to identify equipment as demo, which are excluded from the Contract Penetration snapshot as needed, via a join.

Data is in standard Historical format so historical data can be selected and joined.

 

To select current truth IS_ACTIVE = Y

 

Load Frequency: Monthly
